Rehn Says Spain Has Made Major Progress With Fiscal Measures

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-09-15T09:57:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/rehn-says-spain-has-made-major-progress-with-fiscal-measures.html
Spain  has made major progress with
its fiscal measures, European Union Economic and Monetary
Commissioner  Olli Rehn  told reporters in Brussels today.  The country has reacted swiftly to renewed market tensions,
he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
